{
  "name": "RPlog_Cease-Fire_at_Sullust",
  "title": "Cease-Fire at Sullust",
  "summary": "When the cease-fire over Sullust collapses, the New Republic fleet under Commander Amari Cociena of the Crusader joins a desperate, losing battle against the Imperial fleet that has captured the Star Destroyer Templar, now the Magnificent. In the swirling dogfight, Ghost Squadron pilots Latar Zaff and the Sullustan-born commander Ikihsa Enb'Zik, alongside A-wing pilot Ridge, trade fire with the Imperial ace Admiral Danik Kreldin in his unmistakable red Interceptor and pilots like Blake Lorrent and Simetha. The Chandrilan Captain Mirhoz of the Inquisitor pleads for sanity over an open channel, and after Kreldin recognizes the battle is lost in lives, Cociena accepts terms: the Republic will withdraw if the interdictor's gravity wells are lowered. With heavy hearts, the Republic pilots cover the refugee ships and jump to hyperspace, leaving Zik's home planet of Sullust in Imperial hands.",
